OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1773227361
OL,3,C'We've been hit': Family home after
OL,4,Cmissile intercepted outside hotel in
OL,5,CDubai
OL,7,FA couple who were on their honeymoon
OL,8,Fwith their 3-year-old son have arrived
OL,9,Fback home, after they were trapped in
OL,10,FDubai as war broke out across the
OL,11,FMiddle East.
OL,13,FMatthew McGinn and Layla Hamood, from
OL,14,FLiverpool, had been in Dubai with
OL,15,Ftheir son for one day when an Iranian
OL,16,Fmissile was intercepted outside their
OL,17,Fhotel, with flames reaching their
OL,18,Fsixth floor room.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
