FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1773227361
OL,3,C'We've been hit': Family home after
OL,4,Cmissile intercepted outside hotel in
OL,5,CDubai
OL,7,FMathew said: "I walked towards the
OL,8,Fdouble doors towards the balcony. Next
OL,9,Fminute, almighty explosion with flames
OL,10,Fcoming as high as the balcony."
OL,12,F"The room shook. I ran into the
OL,13,Fbathroom and said to Layla we've been
OL,14,Fhit, get out, we need to leave this
OL,15,Fhotel now because we don't know what's
OL,16,Fcoming in."
OL,18,F"We're panicking at this point because
OL,19,Fit's something that you don't believe
OL,20,Fhas happened, and you don't believe
OL,21,Fwould ever happen to us."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1773227361
OL,3,C'We've been hit': Family home after
OL,4,Cmissile intercepted outside hotel in
OL,5,CDubai
OL,7,FMathew said the family fled to the
OL,8,Fbeach for safety, where they could see
OL,9,Fthe missiles flying in.
OL,11,FIt comes as disruption across the
OL,12,FMiddle East continues, following the
OL,13,Flaunch of the joint US-Israeli
OL,14,Fmilitary operation against Iran.
OL,16,FMathew and Layla said they tried to
OL,17,Fprotect their son in their hotel room,
OL,18,Fsleeping fully clothed in case they
OL,19,Fhad to run.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1773227361
OL,3,C'We've been hit': Family home after
OL,4,Cmissile intercepted outside hotel in
OL,5,CDubai
OL,7,FThey drove to the airport after nine
OL,8,Fdays, just to be told it had been hit,
OL,9,Fand the family's first flight to
OL,10,FFrankfurt didn't leave the runaway,
OL,11,Fwhen the airspace closed, leaving them
OL,12,Fstranded again.
OL,14,FLayla said: "I couldn't believe it had
OL,15,Fhappened to us. It felt like it was
OL,16,Fsomething out of a film. Because i've
OL,17,Fnever experienced anything like that,
OL,18,FI didn't believe it in a way."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1773227361
OL,3,C'We've been hit': Family home after
OL,4,Cmissile intercepted outside hotel in
OL,5,CDubai
OL,7,FLayla, who is originally from Yemen,
OL,8,Fsaid she worries about the lasting
OL,9,Fimpact of the conflict.
OL,11,FShe said: "You look at what people are
OL,12,Fgoing through on a daily basis, and
OL,13,Fwhats been going on on over the last
OL,14,Fthree years in Gaza, in Iran and
OL,15,FIsrael.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
